v 3
d glemb: General location EMB imputation for Stata
d
d glemb adds a user-defined method for Stata's mi impute command.
d It imputes mixed categorical and continuous data using the general
d location model with EMB.
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260519
d Version: 0.1.3
d Requires: Stata 17 or newer
d
f lglemb.mata
f mi_impute_cmd_glemb.ado
f mi_impute_cmd_glemb_parse.ado
f mi_impute_cmd_glemb_cleanup.ado
f mi_impute_glemb.sthlp
f glemb.ado
f glemb.sthlp
f README.md
